OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish Steel jobs at risk 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin plan to shut furnaces   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Steel plans to close down its  
OL,6, blast furnaces in Scunthorpe, putting  
OL,7, up to 2,000 jobs at risk.              
OL,9,FThe business, owned by China's Jingye  
OL,10,FGroup, wants to replace them with two  
OL,11,Felectric arc furnaces - one at         
OL,12,FScunthorpe and one at Teesside.        
OL,14,FThe construction is expected to take   
OL,15,Fbetween two and three years.           
OL,17,FBritish Steel said it aimed to         
OL,18,Ftransform the firm into a "green and   
OL,19,Fsustainable company" and had to look at
OL,20,Fdifferent scenarios to help it do this.
